OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA rather
OL,6,Fcloudy, but mostly dry evening. The
OL,7,Frest of the night will be largely
OL,8,Fcloudy, with a risk of fog developing
OL,9,Ffor Shetland later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FPatchy mist and fog at
OL,12,Ffirst for Shetland. Otherwise mostly
OL,13,Fdry and bright, but rain and
OL,14,Ffreshening winds arriving from the
OL,15,Fsouthwest in the evening.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FAn
OL,18,Funsettled westerly pattern brings
OL,19,Fbright spells and scattered showers
OL,20,Fduring this period, with some sunshine
OL,21,Fat times but often windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
